Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.98,0:01:44.12,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}比魔法还要强大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.69,0:01:50.13,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}我觉得那是无人所能取代的你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.33,0:01:55.42,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}这份Power of Love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.17,0:01:58.76,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}因此 I'll be there for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.96,0:02:01.40,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}我相信着这份羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.55,0:02:06.94,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}你的空虚 你的唇 你那倔强的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.47,0:02:10.03,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}我喜欢 Always I Love you
